### Register Student (Requires Admin)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "email": "student_test@example.com",
  "username": "student_test",
  "password": "password"
}

### Create Admin (Requires Admin)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/admin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "email": "admin_test@example.com",
  "username": "admin_test",
  "password": "password"
}

### Get User Details (Requires Admin, Teacher of student's group, or Owner)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_public_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Current User Profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Change User Password (Requires Admin or Owner)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_public_id}}/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "oldPassword": "old",
  "newPassword": "new"
}

### Change User Password - wrong old password (401 INVALID_OLD_PASSWORD)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_public_id}}/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "oldPassword": "wrong-old-password",
  "newPassword": "new"
}

### Change User Password - unauthenticated (401 UNAUTHORIZED)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_public_id}}/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "old",
  "newPassword": "new"
}

### Change User Password - forbidden for non-owner (403 FORBIDDEN)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_public_id}}/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{other_user_auth_token}}

{
  "oldPassword": "old",
  "newPassword": "new"
}

### Change User Password - validation failed (400 VALIDATION_FAILED)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_public_id}}/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "oldPassword": "",
  "newPassword": ""
}

### Create Teacher (Requires Admin)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/teacher
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "email": "teacher_test@example.com",
  "username": "teacher_test",
  "password": "password"
}

### Update User Profile (Requires Admin or Owner)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_public_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "username": "updated_user"
}

### Delete User (Requires Admin or Owner)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_public_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
